@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_qupgns(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.exp(0.06)
    v1 = (wp.abs((v1 + 0.16 + v1 + 0.53)) - (wp.abs(tmp + 0.41) + (v2 + 0.89 * tmp + 0.28)))
    v1 = 0.71
    v2 = v1
    v2 = ((0.91 + (v2 + 0.60 + v1 + 0.30)) * wp.cos((v1 + 0.79 - v0 + 0.97)))
    tmp = v1
    data[tid] = v0
